        public StringData getChampionRanks(java.lang.String username)
        Getting Champion ranks by player
        Parameters:
        username - This may either be: a.) the Player Name, or b.) the Hi-Rez internally stored player_id (available to API developers via the HiRezGames.getPlayer(String) API method).

        Returns the Rank and Worshippers value for each Champion a player has played.
